    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >持续不断的末日流星雨迫使全世界的人口迁移到地下生活。扮演希尔（Shell），向下挖掘穿越以瓦片为基础的地下世界，探索永恒深渊（Everdeep）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「这款受到16位元美学启发的叙事探索平台游戏，将带你回到那个时代经典作品的纯真与刺激。这里有一个充满活力且动态的世界等待探索，还有许多奇特的角色可以认识，以及各种不同的谜题需要解决。你能发现隐藏在永恒深渊中的秘密吗？」 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你不断下探，你的决定将决定希尔在深渊中的路线，从秘密洞穴到广阔的地下居住区。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/648dd3f344bedd8bdd76ffdf6752d603.poster.avif?t=1752155773\" width=589 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/648dd3f344bedd8bdd76ffdf6752d603.webm?t=1752155773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在路途中，你将遇见拥有独特个性的角色，有时还会有选择性的支线任务。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/fd2675be282616c17fb9a1fe5b598afd.poster.avif?t=1752155773\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/fd2675be282616c17fb9a1fe5b598afd.webm?t=1752155773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/6b929c4d596b1f175a8e97986eb7bd34.poster.avif?t=1752155773\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/6b929c4d596b1f175a8e97986eb7bd34.webm?t=1752155773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在富有氛围的像素艺术和令人回味的配乐中，色调和音乐主题会随着不同地点而变化。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/d9815ff877610fd297663e4dfe1c93ce.poster.avif?t=1752155773\" width=611 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251400/extras/d9815ff877610fd297663e4dfe1c93ce.webm?t=1752155773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
